hopobject.body: Where are you from? six star testosterone booster side effects Throughout the crisis and its aftermath all manner of policies have been justified or put in place in order to stop markets from falling, or to eke out some economic activity from the wealth effect, the portion of paper gains which finds itself recirculating through the economy. Anything to keep the market happy and buoyant. Unfortunately, while those policies work on markets they've not worked so well on the underlying economy.
